home.title: Generate Official Documents in Seconds

home.mobile_desc: Our generator creates perfect PDF417 barcodes that match real driver's licenses. Every detail is encoded correctly to pass any verification system. Works with US, European and international ID formats. Generate single barcodes or bulk batches in seconds.
home.second_title: The leading barcode generator by Russian hackers — now available to everyone

blocks.field_gen_desc: Our tool smartly fills in missing numbers using local and federal guidelines, eliminating manual entry and ensuring seamless barcode creation.

blocks.verif_desc: Our DMV-level barcodes pass top verifiers (BCS, Veriscan, intellicheck, Sumsub) for both online and offline use.
